assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4687c7baa7822b02a25b2ea33953bc7a038f80","tid":116832,"uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>建築界都就黎玩完 先黎話做地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有好多地未發展,邊會玩完? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n批左未?由批到計劃發展再到真係有個地盤 大既都講緊接近十年 你果十年係咪唔洗食飯 最重要係 好多入左行既人比你更有能力爭飯食"},{"pid":"ff0d784c63e6fb7ab9f1039dfca65797643534f0","tid":116832,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:39:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>建築界都就黎玩完 先黎話做地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有好多地未發展,邊會玩完? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n批左未?由批到計劃發展再到真係有個地盤 大既都講緊接近十年 你果十年係咪唔洗食飯 最重要係 好多入左行既人比你更有能力爭飯食</blockquote><br />\n依家慢慢做, 儲下經驗, 十年之後就發發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2787e32e73e5928d9f27032e8e32343c9d4ea5f6","tid":116832,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:54:30.000Z","msg":"發發啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65fee741d5a147df982e2e2c0834d8acf712b4e","tid":116832,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T14:47:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀緊書果陣讀左OSH 文憑<br />\n但無人脈無關係 入唔到行 去面試比個安全經理串到自尊都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家都係係銀行做番自己本科相關既工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見工都要串你？<br />\nshare 吓？"},{"pid":"0980a6753ae40f6ae262f84bab675f58298353f2","tid":116832,"uid":25641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:29:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e4a141b7e15f26538d3e96994ee14b8060f71d2","tid":116832,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讀緊書果陣讀左OSH 文憑<br />\n但無人脈無關係 入唔到行 去面試比個安全經理串到自尊都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家都係係銀行做番自己本科相關既工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見工都要串你？<br />\nshare 吓？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為自己讀果科同安全完全無關 又無地盤工程背景 係咁比佢質我 開頭都懶係誠懇 盡量答自己識既野 之後都技窮加上咁我本身準備唔夠 開始答埋d行野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後都頂唔順佢咁串柒柒 想走 直頭話其實我係為錢 為多條路先讀安全 如果唔請唔好浪費大家時間 之後閃左<br />\n<br />\n如果條友有上高登 應該又會開post屌柒90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我讀full time safety hd<br />\n一次in都未收過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189c1588e09c63f11abab52ee6e8cf42d553b4a2","tid":116832,"uid":82389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:56:56.000Z","msg":"安全佬唔係你想像中咁容易做<br />\n<br />\n1. 一間公司要做夠兩年<br />\n2.要討好上司唔係冇得註冊<br />\n3.唔係下下有督導員跟你 好多時一個主任負責曬地盤所有嘅安全系統 做埋雜工嗰份<br />\n4.即係工程師同個客 老闆中間<br />\n5. 100個工人先要一個主任，好難搵工<br />\n6.我上年有牌 搵左3個月 番左3個月<br />\n7.之後又搵左3個月 番左3個月⋯<br />\n<br />\n利申：做左4年"},{"pid":"78059d9a815d590e3db0cb8d0a2be59c020a070b","tid":116832,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T23:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讀緊書果陣讀左OSH 文憑<br />\n但無人脈無關係 入唔到行 去面試比個安全經理串到自尊都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家都係係銀行做番自己本科相關既工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見工都要串你？<br />\nshare 吓？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為自己讀果科同安全完全無關 又無地盤工程背景 係咁比佢質我 開頭都懶係誠懇 盡量答自己識既野 之後都技窮加上咁我本身準備唔夠 開始答埋d行野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後都頂唔順佢咁串柒柒 想走 直頭話其實我係為錢 為多條路先讀安全 如果唔請唔好浪費大家時間 之後閃左<br />\n<br />\n如果條友有上高登 應該又會開post屌柒90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我讀full time safety hd<br />\n一次in都未收過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未in過就返到工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4549df9824690e6f61ae84ff66419f4fafdea3d4","tid":116832,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T23:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讀緊書果陣讀左OSH 文憑<br />\n但無人脈無關係 入唔到行 去面試比個安全經理串到自尊都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家都係係銀行做番自己本科相關既工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見工都要串你？<br />\nshare 吓？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為自己讀果科同安全完全無關 又無地盤工程背景 係咁比佢質我 開頭都懶係誠懇 盡量答自己識既野 之後都技窮加上咁我本身準備唔夠 開始答埋d行野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後都頂唔順佢咁串柒柒 想走 直頭話其實我係為錢 為多條路先讀安全 如果唔請唔好浪費大家時間 之後閃左<br />\n<br />\n如果條友有上高登 應該又會開post屌柒90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我讀full time safety hd<br />\n一次in都未收過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未in過就返到工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾十歲人唔好咁多幻想啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6600f45606f5447d00b5057a6e589bc3c2a6b55e","tid":116832,"uid":71391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T23:56:52.000Z","msg":"好似係so : workers = 1:50<br />\n<br />\n要得幾多個啫"},{"pid":"b7fbd9b5cfd08e